    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Family containing four genera of about 20 living African species of small, quick primates, and three fossil genera, dating from the Miocene to Holocene. They are sometimes included as a subfamily within the Loridae.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
